data.title: Flannery O'Connor Timeline
data.meta_description: A timeline in the life events of Savannah born novelist Flannery O'Connor
data.text: Novelist Flannery O'Connor was born in Savannah and spent the first 15 years of her life here. Her birthplace on Lafayette Square is a popular Savannah tourist attraction. This timeline of events from her life include her most notable accomplishments. If you would like to learn more, visit our page on Flannery O'Connor and her childhood home.
